"Narrated Abu Huraira:Abu Bakr said, \"By Allah! If they (pay me the Zakat and) withhold even a young (female) goat which they used to pay during the lifetime of Allah's Messenger (ﷺ), I will fight with them for it.\" `Umar said, \"It was nothing but Allah Who opened Abu Bakr's chest towards the decision to fight, and I came to know that his decision was right"